name: BioJS Example
title: BioJS package from CommonJS module installed from NPM
description: An example using a CommonJS NPM module that is part of the [BioJS registry](http://biojs.io/).  Simple barchart to show expression levels across experiments.  Using [homonecloco/biojs-vis-expression-bar](https://github.com/homonecloco/biojs-vis-expression-bar) BioJS visualization module and example data.
